{"tid":2462482,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（吃澳洲的麥...）長江水災後夏糧變豐收  中国大量進口澳洲小麥 比去年同期多4倍","createTime":"2021-03-26T04:32:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T05:28:46.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c85f2a1ab16a2dae0be522bddad7c49860076f0e","tid":2462482,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:32:58.000Z","msg":"儘管中澳兩國關係一再惡化，但中國從澳洲進口的小麥比去年同期多了幾倍。澳洲最新數據顯示，2月份，澳洲谷物的總出口值創下最高單月紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n據《南華早報》報導，今年前兩個月，中國從澳洲進口的小麥比去年同期多了479.3%。此時正值小麥生產大國俄羅斯遭遇乾旱天氣，為了遏制國內糧價上漲，俄羅斯開始限製出口。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲統計局3月24日公布的最新數據顯示，澳洲2月的谷物出口值高達12.88億澳元，是有記錄以來最高的月度出口額。<br />\n<br />\n由於中共對澳洲實施經濟報復，中澳兩國關係一再惡化。澳洲駐華大使弗萊徹（Graham Fletcher）在3月25日的澳中商會簡報中批評北京是一個「靠不住」且「報復心強」的貿易夥伴。<br />\n<br />\n雖然澳洲價值200億澳元商品遭到中共各種限制措施的刁難，但迄今為止，中國仍在大量進口澳洲小麥。去年12月，澳洲谷物出口商向中國出口了60萬噸小麥，創下了澳洲向任一國家單月出口量的最高紀錄，而今年前兩個月出口量也只比去年年底稍低。<br />\n<br />\n儘管遭遇中共的經濟報復和去年的乾旱天氣，澳洲的谷物種植者今年出人意料地迎來大豐收，而且由於谷物價格高企，這個收穫季成爲他們有史以來收入最豐厚的收穫季之一。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">中共在去年7月份宣傳以小麥為主的夏糧總產量創歷史新高；但到了8月份，中共糧食和物資儲備局又承認，主產區小麥的收購減少938萬噸，同比下降近20%。對於這組矛盾的數據，有分析認為中共宣傳產量增加是造假，農民手中已沒有餘糧</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2021/02/GettyImages-1230572869-600x400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2FGettyImages-1230572869-600x400.jpg&h=8107ca9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/3/26/n12836852.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F21%2F3%2F26%2Fn12836852.htm&d=eMoIgPJs71q5KSiTXOS1GitC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=cd350564\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.epochtimes.com/b5/21/3/26/n12836852.htm</a>"},{"pid":"55abdde89fcc8987cf145025add6de5df2117e50","tid":2462482,"uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">以農立国</span></span>"},{"pid":"926e775a3f4b92c5513e448a055de49ebd124158","tid":2462482,"uid":393145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:34:02.000Z","msg":"當年畝產萬斤之後就係困難時期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1d6084d06bdf1574e3702f3bd2fb3c88ff456e","tid":2462482,"uid":65956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55abdde89fcc8987cf145025add6de5df2117e50","tid":2462482,"uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">以農立国</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:37:22.000Z","msg":"以愚立国呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50659e9cb5ef218831a65dae53e8dcb7e81c6a73","tid":2462482,"uid":151074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:38:11.000Z","msg":"小氣国吃澳洲的糧，砸澳洲的碗"},{"pid":"7151f7a40622943fed9ac62d60a79782257162b0","tid":2462482,"uid":157138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:41:22.000Z","msg":"食澳洲既野，照你地邏輯唔可以同澳洲作對架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705118d83c84a5a4fef430d88840ca71aad5e319","tid":2462482,"uid":90820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"要不是中國，澳洲玩完了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7852d6561429e855338855dc6c7a52656e083125","tid":2462482,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7151f7a40622943fed9ac62d60a79782257162b0","tid":2462482,"uid":157138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:41:22.000Z","msg":"食澳洲既野，照你地邏輯唔可以同澳洲作對架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T04:46:41.000Z","msg":"思維<br />\n<br />\n強国係買家或賣家 都係要不是xxx"},{"pid":"ee436de6275b684815d5ffd3748c0e17234a3404","tid":2462482,"uid":28759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:11:24.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">飲水思源</span>"},{"pid":"64ef16bd2c20bc011190f55e360ecd66e45b25cd","tid":2462482,"uid":279440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:24:29.000Z","msg":"可以改食草"},{"pid":"bee24fac5b346510518c02c909424fc9edd9fad5","tid":2462482,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:25:33.000Z","msg":"食邊度嘅麥就係邊度嘅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db40f2ec30b453b91a3ae2303a546b68ba21efa","tid":2462482,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T05:28:46.000Z","msg":"本來中國應該係一個農業國家<br />\n結果俾中共玩到變依賴性強既進口國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n制裁人地同玩死自己有咩分別"}]}